Game.Overview:
BlazeRush is a dynamic vehicular combat game with no health, no levelling and no brakes!
Grab some pals, chopse a car and go kick ass, that's as simple as that!
Adapt your style and tactics to new enemies, obstacles and tracks.
Welcome to the world of furious racing and frantic fun!

Key features:
Up to 4 players locally and up to 8 players online;
Couch vs. couch. Take local players online;
Jump-in multiplayer;
Dozens of tracks on three planets, 16 cars and a variety of cool guns;
Lots of medals for various tricks and antics.
